This torrent may contain a trojan/virus.  When I double clicked the avi, one of my spyware programs alerted me of a malicious attempt. Something in the file wanted to open my windows explorer (buffer overflow). I quarantined the threat, then tried running the avi again and was able to watch it without anymore alerts popping up. Computer seems free of trojans/virus and malware otherwise. The avi's are watchable though.
